dc_title_s: United States National Atlas Federal Land Lines, 1972-2001
dc_description_s: This line shapefile represents the federally owned land features (for example, national parkways and wild and scenic rivers) of the United States. No data exists for Hawaii. This layer is part of the 2014 ESRI Data and Maps collection for ArcGIS 10.2. U.S. National Atlas Federal Land Lines provides the linear federally owned land features for geographic display and analysis at regional and national levels. National Atlas of the United States, ESRI, and U.S. Geological Survey. (2014). United States National Atlas Federal Land Lines, 1972-2001. ESRI.
dc_creator_sm: National Atlas of the United States
